<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FAQ - The Support Pantry Network</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 15px;
        }

        .accordion-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .accordion-button {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 500;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border: none;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .accordion-button:hover {
            background-color: #e9ecef;
        }

        .accordion-collapse {
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .accordion-body p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .accordion-body p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .accordion-collapse.show {
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s ease forwards;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }

            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="bg-light">
        <div class="container py-3">
            <div class="row align-items-center py-3">
                <div class="col-lg-5">
                    <div class="img-container">
                        <img src="/images/mission.png" alt="TSPN Logo" class="img-fluid">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-7">
                    <h1 class="display-5 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
                    <p class="lead text-muted mb-4 text-center">Find answers to common questions about The S Pantry Network below.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white py-5">
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                <!-- What is a pantry? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            What is a pantry?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Pantries are located in local communities and offer heavily discounted food for a small membership fee. Many of the pantries mentioned on this website also provide guidance and support on topics related to food insecurity, such as bills, benefits, unemployment, and mental health, among others.</p>
                            <p>Please contact your local pantry to learn about the latest changes and events!</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- What if I don't have money? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            What if I don't have money?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>If you don't have money, you can still visit the pantry. Each pantry sets its own charge for a weekly shop, ranging from £2.50 to £3.50.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- How many times a week can I visit a pantry? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            How many times a week can I visit a pantry?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>As many times as you need. Please check the opening days and times on the location page.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- How much does it cost? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            How much does it cost?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Each pantry sets its own charge for a weekly shop, ranging from £2.50 to £3.50.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- What do I get for £2.50 - £3.50? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                            What do I get for £2.50 - £3.50?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>You get around £10 – £15 worth of food.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- What kind of produce do our pantries have? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                            What kind of produce do our pantries have?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Our food comes from FareShare Glasgow and the West, which is a franchise of the national organization FareShare UK. FareShare collects surplus food and redistributes it to community food organizations, including the pantries.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Who can use the pantry? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSeven">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseSeven" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSeven">
                            Who can use the pantry?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseSeven" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSeven" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Anyone can use the pantry.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Where are you located? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingEight">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseEight" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseEight">
                            Where are you located?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseEight" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingEight" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Please check the location page for the address and map.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- What are your opening times? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingNine">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseNine" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseNine">
                            What are your opening times?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseNine" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingNine" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Please check the location page for the opening days and times.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Where does your food come from? -->
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTen">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTen" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTen">
                            Where does your food come from?
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTen" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTen" data-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p>Our food comes from FareShare Glasgow and the West, which is a franchise of the national organization FareShare UK. FareShare collects surplus food and redistributes it to community food organizations, including the pantries. To make a pantry work, a large or above FareShare membership must be secured, this is done through an application process to FareShareGWS.</p>
                            <p>It should be noted that TSPN has no control over FareShareGWS membership process.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        $(document).ready(function () {
            $('.accordion-button').click(function () {
                $(this).toggleClass('collapsed');
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>

</html>
